# Architecture

- Three layers per feature: presentation, domain, data.
- Widgets render state and dispatch intents only.
- Business rules live in domain use-cases.
- Repository pattern with interfaces in domain, impls in data.
- Shared UI in `lib/shared/widgets/`.
- Core cross-cutting concerns in `lib/core/`.
